            xmax = 1228.843 
            text = "nor er hot nisht gekent keyn gutn poylish. fun dest vegn hobn zey ibergelebt in Grokhov, dos heyst oykh oyf Shne- oykh UNK oyf di andere zayt Vaysl." 
